snippet.title: STRAY | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Stray is coming to PS5, PS4, and Steam on July 19. Pre-order on Steam: https://bit.ly/StraySteamPreorder_YT

Lost, alone, and separated from family, a stray cat must untangle an ancient mystery to escape a long-forgotten cybercity and find their way home.

Developed by BLUETWELVE. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2022
